REMARK   3 FITTING PROCEDURE : THE ATOMISTIC MODELS OF MONOMERIC SARS-COV-2
REMARK   3  S1 PROTEIN AND A FAB MOLECULE, EXTRACTED FROM PDB ENTRIES 7A92
REMARK   3  AND 5WI9, WERE DOCKED IN THE CRYO-EM MAP USING CHIMERA. THE NTD
REMARK   3  AND THE RBD OF THE SPIKE SUBUNIT WERE REPLACED WITH THE CRYSTAL
REMARK   3  STRUCTURES FROM PDB ENTRIES 7B62 AND 7OAO, RESPECTIVELY. GUIDED
REMARK   3  BY THE CRYO-EM MAP, THE MODEL WAS ADJUSTED AND EXTENDED
REMARK   3  INTERACTIVELY IN COOT AND REFINED USING PHENIX.REAL_SPACE_REFINE.
